1
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:26,960
Zhu.

2
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,439
Did you hear?

3
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:29,840
Your ex-wife

4
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,000
and Xing Wu's mom

5
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,199
ended up at the police station.

6
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,319
What? They went to the station?

7
00:02:34,599 --> 00:02:35,319
How is that possible?

8
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,520
Don't listen to gossip.

9
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,479
Ask around if you don't believe me.

10
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:39,120
Listen,
you finally found

11
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:41,280
a bright student like Qing Ye.

12
00:02:41,439 --> 00:02:42,479
Don't let

13
00:02:42,479 --> 00:02:44,000
family trouble drag her down.

14
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:46,120
Otherwise, she may end up

15
00:02:46,319 --> 00:02:47,199
just like Xing Wu.

16
00:02:55,919 --> 00:02:58,120
Why's the sign broken?

17
00:02:58,159 --> 00:02:59,680
It was fine yesterday.

18
00:03:00,719 --> 00:03:01,759
When bad luck hits,

19
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,919
it all hits at once.

20
00:03:03,159 --> 00:03:03,800
Just my luck.

21
00:03:05,879 --> 00:03:06,680
What's going on?

22
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:07,800
A power outage?

23
00:03:08,639 --> 00:03:09,719
Probably a loose connection.

24
00:03:10,719 --> 00:03:11,599
I'll fix it later.

25
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:13,360
How is Grandma now?

26
00:03:14,199 --> 00:03:15,400
Grandma's in the hospital now.

27
00:03:15,759 --> 00:03:17,080
Shu Han's with her now.

28
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:20,719
Don't worry.
Lanfang.

29
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:21,639
It's okay.

30
00:03:22,759 --> 00:03:23,479
You're back.

31
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,159
What happened, exactly?

32
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,599
Let's talk at the mahjong parlor.

33
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,479
Come on, let's go.
We'll talk there.

34
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:31,719
Are you okay?

35
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,319
What could possibly be wrong?

36
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:35,319
Shu Han is with Grandma.

37
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,080
Quanya and Shu Han

38
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,199
will take turns tonight.

39
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,639
I'll bring some things tomorrow.

40
00:03:42,199 --> 00:03:43,719
The surgery must be expensive.

41
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:45,560
Is there anything I can do?

42
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,199
Don't worry about that.

43
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,280
You're a student.

44
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,599
Just focus on studying.

45
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,680
Why are you back?

46
00:04:40,319 --> 00:04:41,680
Grandma's more important.

47
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:43,160
I just came to check on you.

48
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,439
Do you need any help?

49
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:45,639
I'm fine.
I've got this.

50
00:04:49,399 --> 00:04:50,839
Can you stop trying to

51
00:04:50,839 --> 00:04:52,079
shoulder everything yourself?

52
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:56,600
Your mom may seem carefree,

53
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:58,480
but that's because

54
00:04:58,519 --> 00:05:00,879
I'm just giving myself an out.

55
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:07,639
Grandma's treatment

56
00:05:08,519 --> 00:05:09,600
may be over 10,000 yuan.

57
00:05:12,519 --> 00:05:13,079
I know.

58
00:05:13,759 --> 00:05:14,639
I'll figure it out.

59
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:18,839
I'll figure something out too.

60
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,120
Yufen.
[Lanfang.]

61
00:05:44,279 --> 00:05:45,600
[Why did you leave so suddenly?]

62
00:05:45,879 --> 00:05:47,399
[We know things are hard for you.]

63
00:05:47,759 --> 00:05:48,639
[Don't be embarrassed.]
[Ask us if you need money.]

64
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:50,720
[When you came to the shop,]

65
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,279
[we could all tell.]

66
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:55,199
Well,

67
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,160
I...

68
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,279
[Cici and I talked it over.]

69
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,240
[Cici and I can pool]
[six thousand yuan first.]

70
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:02,079
[The neighbors will]

71
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,199
[help figure out the rest.]

72
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,720
[Don't stress about it, okay?]

73
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:10,079
You know me.

74
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,040
I always stay optimistic.

75
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:26,600
Hello, Dahei.

76
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:29,600
It's me. I need a favor.

77
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:32,759
Here's the thing.

78
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,199
Something happened to Grandma.

79
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:36,480
She's in the hospital.

80
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:40,000
I'm short on money.

81
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,319
Could you

82
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:44,160
lend me five thousand?

83
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,680
If not, three thousand.

84
00:06:45,879 --> 00:06:46,680
Two thousand is fine too.

85
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:50,959
Sure, sure.
No problem.

86
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:55,000
Okay, okay.

87
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:56,720
Thanks. Thank you.

88
00:06:57,199 --> 00:06:57,920
I appreciate it.

89
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:14,680
[Qing Ye.]

90
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,160
[Help me with English.]

91
00:07:16,639 --> 00:07:17,480
[I can pay you.]

92
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:27,879
Hello, Qing Ye.

93
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:29,680
Hello?

94
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,879
About the English tutoring,

95
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,639
still 300 yuan a lesson?

96
00:07:33,759 --> 00:07:34,600
Does that still stand?

97
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,000
Of course.

98
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,959
Okay. I accept.

99
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:39,040
I have conditions too.

100
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:40,480
Name them.

101
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:43,399
Pay a deposit first.

102
00:07:43,959 --> 00:07:45,360
Ten lessons minimum.

103
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:47,319
Book ten, get one free.

104
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:49,079
I pick the time and place.

105
00:07:49,959 --> 00:07:50,600
No problem.

106
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,279
Make it twenty lessons.

107
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:55,800
Okay.

108
00:08:23,959 --> 00:08:25,199
Morning, Qing Ye.

109
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,000
Shu Han.
Get in.

110
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,079
Wait. Didn't we say evenings?

111
00:08:28,079 --> 00:08:29,360
Why are you here now?

112
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,000
Shu Han said it's on her way.

113
00:08:31,079 --> 00:08:32,120
She's taking us to school.

114
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,080
Since I'm picking you up,

115
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,519
I'll drop them at school

116
00:08:36,639 --> 00:08:37,399
then head to the county.

117
00:08:38,759 --> 00:08:39,200
Let's go.

118
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,519
I sent you the new contract.

119
00:08:41,639 --> 00:08:42,679
I changed it

120
00:08:42,679 --> 00:08:43,519
as you asked.
When you have time,

121
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:44,960
read it carefully.

122
00:08:45,759 --> 00:08:46,519
Mr. Ye is

123
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:47,840
really sincere this time.

124
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,000
He wants to offer you

125
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:49,919
a three-year full-time contract.

126
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,120
Think it over.

127
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,159
I've read the contract.
No issues.

128
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:54,399
Print it and start the paperwork.

129
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:54,840
Okay.

130
00:08:55,639 --> 00:08:56,159
Qing Ye.

131
00:08:56,519 --> 00:08:57,360
I have a contract too.

132
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,799
I thought it over last night.

133
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,960
I think we should make

134
00:09:03,519 --> 00:09:04,679
our relationship official.

135
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:05,759
What relationship?

136
00:09:08,879 --> 00:09:09,879
A teacher-student relationship.

137
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,639
And the contract proves it.

138
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,960
Those twenty lessons,

139
00:09:14,159 --> 00:09:15,600
you can't skip a single one.

140
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,240
Not even the two freebies.

141
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:18,799
No refunds either.

142
00:09:20,399 --> 00:09:21,519
You're tutoring him?

143
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:24,000
Since when?

144
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,039
We agreed last night.

145
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,440
We start today.

146
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:28,600
Xing Wu.
Look,

147
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:30,840
You and Shu Han
both work for my dad.

148
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:34,559
I'm a VIP at Xuan Island too.

149
00:09:34,639 --> 00:09:36,399
And Qing Ye is my teacher now.

150
00:09:36,759 --> 00:09:37,360
Guess I'm really meant

151
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,480
to be part of

152
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,159
your Xuan Island family.

153
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,919
Get in already.

154
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,039
Coming.

155
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,879
Ye Yingjian, hurry up.

156
00:10:10,919 --> 00:10:11,720
Almost. Wait for me.

157
00:10:12,159 --> 00:10:13,360
Qing Ye, remember to sign it.

158
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:20,480
Qing Ye.

159
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,320
Ye Yingjian's contract.

160
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:24,639
Do you have to?

161
00:10:28,679 --> 00:10:30,159
Then Shu Han's contract,

162
00:10:30,639 --> 00:10:31,480
Do you have to?

163
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:42,279
Your job here
is to study hard

164
00:10:43,039 --> 00:10:44,279
and leave after the gaokao.

165
00:10:45,279 --> 00:10:46,639
Tutoring is just extra.

166
00:10:47,039 --> 00:10:48,120
It won't affect my studies.

167
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,279
I know you're trying

168
00:10:51,679 --> 00:10:52,399
to help Grandma.
Exactly.

169
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:54,519
You know

170
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,440
I can't just stand by.

171
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:57,320
But my family's problems

172
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,399
can't be solved

173
00:10:58,399 --> 00:10:59,200
with a few thousand yuan.

174
00:11:06,039 --> 00:11:06,960
In a week,

175
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,480
my enrollment will be canceled.

176
00:11:08,879 --> 00:11:09,639
Tell Zhu Feng
to cancel it.

177
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,759
You're really not going back?

178
00:11:16,279 --> 00:11:16,840
I'm not.

179
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,440
Liu Nian.

180
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:11,519
Lanfang.

181
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:15,039
This is an IOU.

182
00:12:15,759 --> 00:12:16,399
Take it.

183
00:12:16,799 --> 00:12:18,440
I'll pay back every cent.

184
00:12:19,159 --> 00:12:21,000
For now, ask your friends

185
00:12:21,039 --> 00:12:21,879
about some odd jobs.

186
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,240
When we reopen,

187
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:24,120
I'll let you know.

188
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:25,840
Lanfang,

189
00:12:26,159 --> 00:12:27,279
I haven't worked these days.

190
00:12:27,519 --> 00:12:28,360
Can you deduct
those days?

191
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:32,120
You won't lose a cent of your pay.

192
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,279
Take it. Don't worry.

193
00:12:33,879 --> 00:12:34,879
I have money.

194
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:36,960
Then, Lanfang,

195
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:38,879
when can we reopen?

196
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,200
I believe

197
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,600
it'll be very soon.

198
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:02,080
Who is it?

199
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:04,120
Coming.

200
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:07,559
Xiaolian.

201
00:13:09,039 --> 00:13:10,840
It's me. I came to see you.

202
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:12,559
Open the door. Let me in.

203
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:13,320
Xiaolian.

204
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,519
Xiaolian, I really came

205
00:13:14,519 --> 00:13:15,679
to apologize

206
00:13:15,679 --> 00:13:17,159
and make things right.

207
00:13:22,159 --> 00:13:22,600
Well,

208
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,200
Xiaolian, I'll go now.

209
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:26,879
I brought you some food.

210
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,200
I'll leave it at the door.

211
00:13:28,679 --> 00:13:30,399
Remember to eat it.

212
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:40,399
Xiaolian.

213
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:41,879
Xiaolian.

214
00:13:43,679 --> 00:13:44,759
Xiaolian, Xia...

215
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,200
Xiaolian.

216
00:13:47,519 --> 00:13:47,919
This...

217
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:54,600
I paid good money for this.

218
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,399
Pass out the papers.

219
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:22,200
Mr. Zhu.

220
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,200
Can you sign this for me?

221
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:28,000
A leave slip?
Yes.

222
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:30,320
I'd like to ask

223
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:31,720
to miss evening study this week.

224
00:14:32,039 --> 00:14:33,200
Grandma's in the hospital.

225
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:35,159
I need to stay with her.

226
00:14:35,519 --> 00:14:36,279
But I promise
I won't fall behind.

227
00:14:37,799 --> 00:14:38,240
Okay.

228
00:14:42,759 --> 00:14:43,480
Thank you, Mr. Zhu.

229
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,200
Right, Qing Ye.

230
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:51,360
About what I told you last time,

231
00:14:51,879 --> 00:14:53,080
how did your talk with Xing Wu go?

232
00:14:55,519 --> 00:14:56,600
Grandma needs care.

233
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:57,840
Xuan Island has to fix issues.

234
00:14:58,759 --> 00:15:00,000
Everything at home is a mess.

235
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:03,440
Got it.
Okay. Go ahead.

236
00:15:37,759 --> 00:15:38,519
Wu.

237
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,320
Take a break.

238
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:42,639
Grandma can rest now.

239
00:15:43,759 --> 00:15:44,279
Go to sleep.

240
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,440
[Your enrollment's canceled.]

241
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:01,000
[Doesn't that feel like a waste?]

242
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:01,639
Qing Ye.

243
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:03,080
Why did you leave?

244
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:04,359
Skipping evening study?

245
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:06,160
I got permission.

246
00:17:06,680 --> 00:17:07,319
Leave?

247
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,079
Did something happen?

248
00:17:10,759 --> 00:17:11,400
Not really.

249
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:15,079
You suddenly want to tutor me

250
00:17:16,279 --> 00:17:17,480
because I'm already good,

251
00:17:17,759 --> 00:17:18,680
so I can get even better,

252
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:19,960
so we can both

253
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:21,200
get into good colleges together?

254
00:17:26,319 --> 00:17:27,440
You're still unhappy.

255
00:17:28,160 --> 00:17:29,279
Are you short of money?

256
00:17:31,079 --> 00:17:31,799
Is there anything

257
00:17:31,799 --> 00:17:32,920
money can't solve?

258
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:42,400
You think the same as I used to.

259
00:17:43,519 --> 00:17:44,599
But lately, life

260
00:17:44,599 --> 00:17:45,440
has taught me

261
00:17:46,640 --> 00:17:47,599
that some problems

262
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:49,759
money just can't fix.

263
00:17:52,119 --> 00:17:53,079
There are things
money can't fix?

264
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:02,079
I used to be confused

265
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:04,319
why he couldn't choose

266
00:18:04,319 --> 00:18:06,079
his own life and fate.

267
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:08,599
Later, I put myself

268
00:18:08,599 --> 00:18:09,240
in his shoes.

269
00:18:10,119 --> 00:18:10,960
If I were him,

270
00:18:11,960 --> 00:18:13,000
would I do any better?

271
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:17,000
Maybe I'd make the same choice.

272
00:18:19,119 --> 00:18:19,640
He?

273
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:21,119
Who's he?

274
00:18:24,680 --> 00:18:25,480
Someone in my family.

275
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:27,599
Family?

276
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:29,759
I don't know how to comfort you.

277
00:18:30,759 --> 00:18:31,359
And I don't know

278
00:18:31,359 --> 00:18:32,640
how to help your family.

279
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:34,079
But I know

280
00:18:34,519 --> 00:18:35,680
if it were me,

281
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:38,400
I'd stay by her side,

282
00:18:39,839 --> 00:18:40,960
even if I could do nothing.

283
00:18:46,319 --> 00:18:47,720
Thank you for telling me.

284
00:18:49,279 --> 00:18:50,000
I'll go now.

285
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:34,480
Grandma.
Ye.

286
00:19:35,920 --> 00:19:36,720
You're here.

287
00:19:37,359 --> 00:19:37,720
Better?
Did you get wet?

288
00:19:38,799 --> 00:19:39,880
I'm fine. I'm fine.

289
00:19:41,079 --> 00:19:42,039
How are you feeling?

290
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:43,279
Good.

291
00:19:43,640 --> 00:19:44,240
Wu

292
00:19:44,559 --> 00:19:46,079
has taken care of me every day.

293
00:19:46,640 --> 00:19:47,720
I'm recovering very well.

294
00:19:48,640 --> 00:19:49,599
That's good.

295
00:19:50,039 --> 00:19:51,440
I brought you fish soup.

296
00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:53,039
Have more later.

297
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:53,839
Get some calcium.
It helps you heal.

298
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:55,720
Okay.

299
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:56,960
All right.
Good.

300
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:00,799
Here.

301
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:02,519
Okay, here.

302
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,960
Hot fish soup.

303
00:20:11,519 --> 00:20:12,200
Here, try it.
Okay.

304
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:13,519
Taste okay?

305
00:20:18,519 --> 00:20:19,279
Delicious.

306
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:23,680
Lanfang made this, right?

307
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:26,480
How did you know?

308
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:29,480
I've eaten her cooking for decades.

309
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:30,559
How could I not know?

310
00:20:32,599 --> 00:20:33,160
Look.

311
00:20:34,039 --> 00:20:35,599
When she makes fish soup,

312
00:20:36,039 --> 00:20:38,000
there's not a single fishbone.

313
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:43,960
Grandma.

314
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:46,640
Auntie asked me to tell you

315
00:20:47,200 --> 00:20:49,039
after she deals with He Xiaolian,

316
00:20:49,319 --> 00:20:50,240
she'll come to you.

317
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:51,799
Okay.

318
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:55,799
Drink it while it's warm.

319
00:23:07,279 --> 00:23:07,680
Here.

320
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:09,119
I'm sorry.

321
00:23:09,839 --> 00:23:10,720
Xing Wu's mom, why are you here?

322
00:23:11,480 --> 00:23:11,880
I...

323
00:23:12,880 --> 00:23:13,839
I came to bring you soup.

324
00:23:14,880 --> 00:23:16,200
Look, it's noon.

325
00:23:16,200 --> 00:23:17,720
Why are you still eating instant noodles?

326
00:23:17,960 --> 00:23:19,839
You do so much for your students.

327
00:23:20,039 --> 00:23:21,279
Have some soup.

328
00:23:21,559 --> 00:23:23,000
It smells good.

329
00:23:24,119 --> 00:23:24,799
You drink it.

330
00:23:26,160 --> 00:23:27,039
You need something, right?

331
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:30,720
Yes. I need your help.

332
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:33,279
I can guess

333
00:23:33,279 --> 00:23:33,839
what it is.

334
00:23:36,079 --> 00:23:36,599
Well...

335
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:39,720
Xiaolian keeps avoiding me,

336
00:23:40,079 --> 00:23:41,279
but I really need

337
00:23:41,319 --> 00:23:42,079
to see her, just once.

338
00:23:42,559 --> 00:23:44,119
so I came to ask for help.

339
00:23:44,119 --> 00:23:44,759
No problem.

340
00:23:45,359 --> 00:23:46,480
He Xiaolian and I

341
00:23:46,480 --> 00:23:47,880
lived together for years.

342
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:48,799
Her temper, her ways,
I know them best.

343
00:23:50,240 --> 00:23:50,920
How about this?

344
00:23:51,119 --> 00:23:52,079
I'll go with you.

345
00:23:52,599 --> 00:23:53,720
You'll come with me?

346
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:55,640
It's fine.

347
00:23:55,759 --> 00:23:56,960
Thank you, Mr. Zhu.

348
00:23:57,160 --> 00:23:57,640
Thank you.
It's fine.

349
00:23:58,720 --> 00:23:59,319
Think of it
for Xing Wu's sake.

350
00:24:08,720 --> 00:24:09,640
Xiaolian is home.

351
00:24:10,599 --> 00:24:11,200
Xiaolian.

352
00:24:12,640 --> 00:24:13,160
Xiaolian.

353
00:24:13,200 --> 00:24:14,359
Xia... Xiaolian. Xiaolian.

354
00:24:14,359 --> 00:24:14,799
Xiaolian.
Let go.

355
00:24:15,839 --> 00:24:16,359
Xiaolian.

356
00:24:16,759 --> 00:24:17,640
We need to talk.

357
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:18,640
Li Lanfang,

358
00:24:18,839 --> 00:24:20,640
my student Xing Wu's mother.

359
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:21,599
Xiaolian.

360
00:24:22,079 --> 00:24:22,880
I'm sorry.

361
00:24:23,319 --> 00:24:23,759
Well...

362
00:24:24,240 --> 00:24:25,920
I came to bring you money.

363
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:27,799
That's all?

364
00:24:28,079 --> 00:24:28,880
Not 30,000?

365
00:24:30,759 --> 00:24:32,119
It isn't thirty thousand.

366
00:24:33,119 --> 00:24:35,519
Your medical bill was 1,500 yuan.

367
00:24:35,720 --> 00:24:36,960
The rest is yours

368
00:24:37,079 --> 00:24:37,920
to spend as you like.
Go ahead.

369
00:24:38,960 --> 00:24:40,519
We agreed on thirty thousand.

370
00:24:40,799 --> 00:24:41,440
Xiaolian.

371
00:24:42,759 --> 00:24:44,680
I scraped this money together

372
00:24:44,680 --> 00:24:45,359
from everywhere.

373
00:24:45,880 --> 00:24:48,000
My shop is closed.

374
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:49,000
And my mother-in-law

375
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:50,200
fell ill and is in the hospital.

376
00:24:50,559 --> 00:24:51,720
She needs money too.

377
00:24:52,519 --> 00:24:55,079
My family can't offer any more.

378
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:57,200
We can't pay thirty thousand.

379
00:24:57,960 --> 00:24:59,359
None of this is easy.

380
00:24:59,759 --> 00:25:00,319
Besides,

381
00:25:00,799 --> 00:25:02,519
Your allergy looks nearly gone.

382
00:25:02,599 --> 00:25:04,000
Your tattooed brows look nice too.

383
00:25:04,079 --> 00:25:04,480
You'll be fine.
Mind your own business.

384
00:25:06,680 --> 00:25:07,240
Li Lanfang.

385
00:25:08,119 --> 00:25:09,079
If you can't pay 30,000,

386
00:25:09,079 --> 00:25:10,160
we're done talking.

387
00:25:10,279 --> 00:25:10,720
Leave.
Xiaolian.

388
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,440
I'm begging you.

389
00:25:12,519 --> 00:25:14,319
Take this for now.

390
00:25:14,599 --> 00:25:16,039
Don't waste your breath.

391
00:25:16,039 --> 00:25:16,480
Go.

392
00:25:16,480 --> 00:25:17,599
I'll do whatever you ask.

393
00:25:17,799 --> 00:25:18,640
I'll kneel.

394
00:25:19,039 --> 00:25:19,920
I'll kneel.

395
00:25:20,119 --> 00:25:20,640
You...

396
00:25:20,720 --> 00:25:22,440
I... I'm sorry, Xiaolian.

397
00:25:22,759 --> 00:25:23,240
Li Lanfang.
Come on, get up.

398
00:25:24,119 --> 00:25:24,720
He Xiaolian.

399
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:26,079
What are you doing?
Zhu Feng.

400
00:25:43,079 --> 00:25:44,799
That's enough.

401
00:25:57,359 --> 00:25:57,839
Fine.

402
00:25:59,279 --> 00:26:00,240
Let's leave it at that.

403
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:02,720
Come on. It's okay now.
Come on.

404
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:06,319
That's settled.

405
00:26:06,359 --> 00:26:07,000
Settled.

406
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:24,440
Here, Xing Wu's mom.

407
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:25,599
Mr. Zhu, it's so hot.
Have some milk tea.

408
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:27,240
Thank you.

409
00:26:30,799 --> 00:26:32,279
My students love this.

410
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:33,759
It's good.

411
00:26:34,559 --> 00:26:35,119
Mr. Zhu.

412
00:26:36,279 --> 00:26:36,720
I...

413
00:26:37,640 --> 00:26:38,319
I need to thank you.

414
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:40,279
You mean back there?

415
00:26:42,279 --> 00:26:43,400
I could've

416
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:44,839
knelt alone.

417
00:26:45,160 --> 00:26:47,160
But you got scolded too.

418
00:26:47,240 --> 00:26:47,680
You really...

419
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:49,599
It's settled. That's what matters.

420
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:50,640
I don't mind.

421
00:26:51,359 --> 00:26:52,039
You don't know yet.

422
00:26:52,039 --> 00:26:53,440
It's not my first

423
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:54,599
kneeling before Xiaolian.

424
00:26:58,599 --> 00:26:59,599
Xiaolian, you know,

425
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:00,759
isn't a bad person.

426
00:27:01,079 --> 00:27:02,920
She just has a fierce temper.

427
00:27:03,359 --> 00:27:04,440
And I'm too soft.

428
00:27:04,599 --> 00:27:06,279
She always says, Zhu Feng,

429
00:27:06,519 --> 00:27:07,359
as a grown man,

430
00:27:07,359 --> 00:27:08,759
why are you always so meek?

431
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:10,279
A man should show some backbone.

432
00:27:10,359 --> 00:27:11,079
Don't I know that?

433
00:27:11,759 --> 00:27:13,319
Of course I do.

434
00:27:14,359 --> 00:27:15,480
The thing is,

435
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:16,680
at home,
it's not about

436
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:18,319
who's right.

437
00:27:19,039 --> 00:27:20,079
When life gets real,

438
00:27:20,359 --> 00:27:21,319
I know when to bend.

439
00:27:22,160 --> 00:27:22,720
My dreams?
No place for them.

440
00:27:24,839 --> 00:27:26,680
Apologizing isn't giving in.

441
00:27:26,880 --> 00:27:28,759
It's winning by yielding.

442
00:27:29,279 --> 00:27:30,200
But

443
00:27:30,240 --> 00:27:31,519
He Xiaolian is too tough.

444
00:27:31,599 --> 00:27:32,359
I was no match for her.

445
00:27:33,440 --> 00:27:34,119
Mr. Zhu.

446
00:27:34,240 --> 00:27:35,400
Somehow, everything

447
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:36,200
you say

448
00:27:36,200 --> 00:27:37,759
sounds reasonable.

449
00:27:37,839 --> 00:27:38,279
Yes.

450
00:27:38,599 --> 00:27:39,880
That's what teachers do.

451
00:27:41,039 --> 00:27:42,039
Actually, Xing Wu's mom,

452
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:43,480
I really admire you.

453
00:27:44,960 --> 00:27:45,640
Admire me?

454
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:48,000
Look at the mess
I've made of my life.

455
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:49,799
What's there to admire?

456
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:53,480
Ever heard of trigonometric functions?

457
00:27:54,839 --> 00:27:55,359
What?

458
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:58,599
Trig functions.

459
00:27:58,599 --> 00:27:59,920
They move in cycles,

460
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:00,880
with a certain rhythm.

461
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:02,400
Peaks and valleys

462
00:28:02,440 --> 00:28:03,599
take turns.

463
00:28:04,319 --> 00:28:05,599
Life is a little like that.

464
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:06,640
Look at you.

465
00:28:06,680 --> 00:28:07,720
Right now, maybe

466
00:28:07,720 --> 00:28:08,960
you're at a low point.

467
00:28:09,960 --> 00:28:10,680
But I believe

468
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:12,200
as long as you

469
00:28:12,240 --> 00:28:13,839
keep going with hope,

470
00:28:14,640 --> 00:28:15,880
you'll come out of it

471
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:16,839
and get back

472
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:18,279
on an upward curve.

473
00:28:19,079 --> 00:28:20,359
Mr. Zhu, I get it.

474
00:28:20,599 --> 00:28:21,480
You mean

475
00:28:21,480 --> 00:28:23,160
my luck may turn soon.

476
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:24,759
More or less.

477
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:27,119
Hope your words come true.

478
00:28:27,559 --> 00:28:27,920
Well...

479
00:28:29,319 --> 00:28:31,200
Sea Goddess, bless me.

480
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:32,559
Bless me, Li Lanfang.

481
00:28:32,599 --> 00:28:34,119
Please turn my luck around.

482
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:36,200
Mr. Zhu.

483
00:28:36,519 --> 00:28:37,400
When you come by,

484
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:38,680
I'll do your hair for free.

485
00:28:39,599 --> 00:28:40,400
That wouldn't be right.
You've had it hard too.

486
00:28:41,519 --> 00:28:43,079
If you really want to thank me,

487
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:44,480
then do this.

488
00:28:44,759 --> 00:28:45,960
Have Xing Wu thank me at school.

489
00:28:49,599 --> 00:28:50,920
The way Wu is now

490
00:28:51,400 --> 00:28:52,079
is my fault
as his mother.

491
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:54,359
Don't say that.

492
00:28:55,079 --> 00:28:56,400
Xing Wu is a good kid.

493
00:28:57,440 --> 00:28:58,079
I just think
it's a shame if he quits school.

494
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:01,200
A child's future

495
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:01,720
can't be ruined

496
00:29:01,720 --> 00:29:03,240
by adult problems.

497
00:29:03,920 --> 00:29:04,599
Don't you agree?

498
00:29:06,720 --> 00:29:07,240
Yes.

499
00:29:12,640 --> 00:29:14,359
Since I'm helping,

500
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:15,839
let me help all the way.

501
00:29:16,480 --> 00:29:16,920
Sure.
Careful.

502
00:29:18,119 --> 00:29:18,519
Okay.

503
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:22,319
Xing Wu's mom.

504
00:29:23,039 --> 00:29:23,920
This next song
is for you.

505
00:29:25,480 --> 00:29:25,920
Great.

506
00:29:59,920 --> 00:30:00,680
I'm back.

507
00:30:00,960 --> 00:30:01,640
You're back.

508
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:04,839
Zhu told me

509
00:30:05,319 --> 00:30:06,759
you settled the compensation.

510
00:30:08,839 --> 00:30:09,799
He told you that?

511
00:30:12,119 --> 00:30:14,079
Why does he tell you

512
00:30:14,160 --> 00:30:15,359
all my embarrassing stories?

513
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:16,359
Embarrassing?

514
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,039
How did he say it?

515
00:30:22,599 --> 00:30:23,240
He said

516
00:30:23,799 --> 00:30:25,359
you were a rose of steel,

517
00:30:26,759 --> 00:30:28,599
turning back the tide

518
00:30:28,640 --> 00:30:30,079
and bracing a crumbling mansion.

519
00:30:33,440 --> 00:30:34,839
I only got the first half.

520
00:30:35,480 --> 00:30:36,359
Well...

521
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:37,920
the second half is right too.

522
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:40,319
By the way,
Grandma gets out

523
00:30:41,799 --> 00:30:42,839
this weekend, right?

524
00:30:43,839 --> 00:30:45,000
The doctor says she's doing well.

525
00:30:45,160 --> 00:30:45,640
This weekend,
she can rest at home.

526
00:30:47,039 --> 00:30:47,599
That's great.

527
00:30:47,960 --> 00:30:48,880
I've been busy lately
getting the permit.

528
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:51,319
I'll get her room

529
00:30:51,319 --> 00:30:51,960
ready in a bit.
I'll do it.

530
00:30:53,119 --> 00:30:53,599
Also,

531
00:30:53,720 --> 00:30:55,440
I ordered a new

532
00:30:55,599 --> 00:30:56,200
roll-up banner.

533
00:30:56,480 --> 00:30:57,880
We're reopening soon, right?

534
00:30:57,920 --> 00:30:58,680
When you have time,

535
00:30:58,680 --> 00:31:00,000
pick it up for me.

536
00:31:00,519 --> 00:31:00,880
Okay.

537
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:10,440
Coming.

538
00:31:11,119 --> 00:31:11,599
Coming.

539
00:31:20,359 --> 00:31:21,319
She's back home.

540
00:31:21,519 --> 00:31:22,000
Wu.

541
00:31:23,599 --> 00:31:24,119
Mom.

542
00:31:24,720 --> 00:31:25,519
Careful. Careful.

543
00:31:26,119 --> 00:31:27,200
Careful, Mom. Don't rush.

544
00:31:27,720 --> 00:31:28,400
You're back.

545
00:31:29,119 --> 00:31:29,519
Careful.
Careful.

546
00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:31,400
Thank you, sir.

547
00:31:32,839 --> 00:31:33,319
Ye.

548
00:31:34,160 --> 00:31:35,119
Okay, thanks. We're home.

549
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:36,079
Mom. Mom.
Lanfang.

550
00:31:37,039 --> 00:31:37,519
Mom.
How are you?

551
00:31:38,519 --> 00:31:39,240
You okay?
Good.

552
00:31:40,599 --> 00:31:41,359
Listen,

553
00:31:41,599 --> 00:31:43,240
everything is settled now.

554
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,119
The business license too.

555
00:31:45,279 --> 00:31:45,640
Look.

556
00:31:45,839 --> 00:31:46,799
We've even put up

557
00:31:46,839 --> 00:31:48,359
the reopening sign.

558
00:31:49,400 --> 00:31:50,400
That's wonderful.

559
00:31:51,039 --> 00:31:52,519
No more foolish mistakes.

560
00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:53,480
No, no.
Never again.

561
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:56,279
Then...

562
00:31:56,519 --> 00:31:57,599
let's take a photo.

563
00:31:57,680 --> 00:31:58,200
Sure. Good.
As a keepsake.

564
00:31:59,240 --> 00:31:59,759
Okay, Grandma.
Okay.

565
00:32:00,279 --> 00:32:00,680
Come on.

566
00:32:00,759 --> 00:32:02,039
Everyone, get ready.

567
00:32:02,039 --> 00:32:03,599
I'll count down. Three, two, one.

568
00:32:03,799 --> 00:32:04,599
Okay, okay.

569
00:32:04,599 --> 00:32:06,799
Three, two, one.

570
00:32:07,079 --> 00:32:08,680
Cheese.

571
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:09,400
One more.

572
00:32:10,319 --> 00:32:12,519
Three, two, one.

573
00:32:12,599 --> 00:32:14,279
Cheese.

574
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,440
Check it. Is it straight?

575
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:18,079
Crooked.

576
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:19,400
No, it's crooked.

577
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:20,960
Wait. Is it straight?

578
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:22,920
It's crooked, son.

579
00:32:23,599 --> 00:32:24,079
Is it straight?

580
00:32:24,759 --> 00:32:25,920
Just right.

581
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:26,839
Good, good, good.
Good.

582
00:32:27,839 --> 00:32:28,319
Grandma knows.

583
00:32:31,920 --> 00:32:32,599
This photo

584
00:32:32,799 --> 00:32:34,359
makes me feel at ease.

585
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:35,839
The shop

586
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:37,160
will only get better.

587
00:32:37,359 --> 00:32:39,240
When family stands united, all goes well.

588
00:32:39,839 --> 00:32:40,359
Exactly.
Auntie.

589
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:43,279
With that optimism,

590
00:32:43,599 --> 00:32:45,440
you can make anything work.

591
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:46,720
Lanfang,

592
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:47,759
I believe in you.

593
00:32:47,759 --> 00:32:48,880
You'll lead Xuan Island

594
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:49,799
bigger and stronger.

595
00:32:50,039 --> 00:32:50,440
Good.
Bigger, stronger.

596
00:32:51,240 --> 00:32:51,599
Yes.
Bigger and stronger.

597
00:32:52,599 --> 00:32:53,599
Bigger and stronger!

598
00:32:53,640 --> 00:32:54,240
Good, good.

599
00:33:02,680 --> 00:33:03,119
Here.

600
00:33:07,599 --> 00:33:09,160
The weather changes so fast.

601
00:33:09,319 --> 00:33:10,680
It was sunny just now.

602
00:33:11,079 --> 00:33:12,079
Then it just started raining.

603
00:33:12,759 --> 00:33:13,880
Maybe life is like that.

604
00:33:14,599 --> 00:33:15,319
One second,

605
00:33:16,039 --> 00:33:16,799
the sky is clear.

606
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:18,279
the next, a storm.

607
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:21,599
So, Boss Xing,

608
00:33:21,799 --> 00:33:22,359
when do you plan
to start at the county office?

609
00:33:25,519 --> 00:33:26,160
Not sure yet.

610
00:33:28,799 --> 00:33:30,200
Things got delayed because of Grandma.

611
00:33:32,200 --> 00:33:32,720
Wait.

612
00:33:35,039 --> 00:33:35,519
What?

613
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,400
My Mom still trying to get me back to school?

614
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:44,799
If taking the county job

615
00:33:45,640 --> 00:33:46,880
is the best choice

616
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:47,920
you can make now,

617
00:33:48,920 --> 00:33:49,960
I won't object.

618
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:54,880
No more school talk?

619
00:33:55,599 --> 00:33:56,079
No more.

620
00:33:56,759 --> 00:33:57,200
Why?

621
00:33:59,480 --> 00:34:00,480
Because I believe in you.

622
00:34:01,319 --> 00:34:02,400
Whichever road you take,

623
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:04,880
even through a storm,

624
00:34:06,039 --> 00:34:06,720
you'll still reach
your own Rome.

625
00:34:08,599 --> 00:34:09,480
And I promise,

626
00:34:10,239 --> 00:34:11,960
whatever decision you make,

627
00:34:12,599 --> 00:34:14,400
I'll stand by you all the way.

628
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:17,440
Got it.

629
00:34:54,599 --> 00:34:55,760
What's with her?

630
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:56,920
That's wild.
Look.

631
00:34:59,639 --> 00:35:00,760
Wasn't her family poor?

632
00:35:01,039 --> 00:35:02,159
So she's a rich kid?

633
00:35:02,239 --> 00:35:03,840
And still had the nerve to claim aid?

634
00:35:03,920 --> 00:35:04,920
Her family has a criminal record.

635
00:35:05,320 --> 00:35:06,760
Can she still take civil service exams?

636
00:35:06,920 --> 00:35:08,679
Her dad can't explain all that money.

637
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:09,880
She can't be clean either.

638
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:10,599
Look. That's her.

639
00:35:11,199 --> 00:35:11,679
It's her.

640
00:35:13,880 --> 00:35:14,360
Qing Ye.

641
00:35:15,079 --> 00:35:15,519
Qing Ye.

642
00:35:16,360 --> 00:35:17,199
Something happened.

643
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:18,400
What happened?

644
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:19,679
Did you see the school forum?

645
00:35:20,199 --> 00:35:20,960
What post?

646
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:42,400
Stop combing it.

647
00:35:42,400 --> 00:35:44,159
Combing only makes it look dog-chewed.

648
00:35:46,079 --> 00:35:47,599
A dog did get to it.

649
00:35:48,239 --> 00:35:48,800
Who cut it?
I'll avoid it.

650
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:12,519
Want some? Dried at home.

651
00:36:16,599 --> 00:36:17,440
Aren't you afraid of me?

652
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:18,480
No.

653
00:36:19,039 --> 00:36:20,599
They believe every rumor.

654
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:21,599
I don't.

655
00:36:35,280 --> 00:36:35,760
Shi Min.

656
00:36:36,639 --> 00:36:37,079
Qing Ye.
Come.

657
00:36:38,119 --> 00:36:39,079
I saved you a seat. Hurry.

658
00:36:41,119 --> 00:36:41,599
Drumstick.

659
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:51,119
What are you doing?

660
00:36:51,159 --> 00:36:52,440
Are you blind?

661
00:36:52,760 --> 00:36:54,199
Why bump into her on purpose?

662
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:55,800
Sorry.

663
00:36:56,159 --> 00:36:57,000
Are you okay?

664
00:37:00,920 --> 00:37:02,119
Sorry.

665
00:37:03,119 --> 00:37:04,199
I didn't mean it either.

666
00:37:04,360 --> 00:37:05,000
It was an accident.
Are you crazy?

667
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:07,000
You did it on purpose.

668
00:37:07,039 --> 00:37:08,360
We didn't mean it.

669
00:37:08,519 --> 00:37:09,000
Qing Ye.

670
00:37:09,199 --> 00:37:10,039
You stained

671
00:37:10,079 --> 00:37:11,079
Li Wenhui's suit.

672
00:37:11,199 --> 00:37:12,400
Everyone saw it.

673
00:37:12,599 --> 00:37:13,599
Right?

674
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:14,840
Yes.
Bullshit.

675
00:37:15,599 --> 00:37:16,440
Forget it, Fang Lei.

676
00:37:16,519 --> 00:37:17,639
She's got thugs behind her.

677
00:37:17,719 --> 00:37:18,519
We can't mess with her.

678
00:37:19,039 --> 00:37:20,199
Got a problem? Come at me.

679
00:37:20,480 --> 00:37:21,679
Don't drag others in.

680
00:37:22,320 --> 00:37:23,360
Then you bullied

681
00:37:23,360 --> 00:37:24,639
Fang Lei and the others.

682
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:25,599
What about that?

683
00:37:26,239 --> 00:37:26,760
Me?

684
00:37:27,159 --> 00:37:28,039
I bullied them?

685
00:37:28,960 --> 00:37:31,000
Zhu, Zhu, Zhu...

686
00:37:31,639 --> 00:37:32,079
Mr. Zhu.
What's wrong?

687
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:34,800
Qing Ye is in the cafeteria,

688
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:36,840
fighting with someone.

689
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:37,519
You cut

690
00:37:37,519 --> 00:37:38,639
both their hair

691
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:39,760
and threatened them

692
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:40,719
not to tell anyone.

693
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:42,039
That's not bullying?

694
00:37:43,760 --> 00:37:44,280
Fang Lei.

695
00:37:44,400 --> 00:37:45,320
Am I lying?

696
00:37:46,679 --> 00:37:47,119
I...

697
00:37:47,239 --> 00:37:48,239
it's true.

698
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:49,239
Look at Fang Lei's hair.

699
00:37:49,280 --> 00:37:50,440
Look what they did to it.

700
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:52,000
You started it.

701
00:37:52,159 --> 00:37:52,760
When I'm bullied,

702
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:54,079
I can't fight back?

703
00:37:55,199 --> 00:37:56,280
You scratched her hand, right?

704
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:57,679
Isn't that bullying too?

705
00:37:58,119 --> 00:37:58,960
It was self-defense.
Believe what you want.

706
00:38:00,679 --> 00:38:01,599
Stop right there.

707
00:38:02,760 --> 00:38:03,599
Fang Lei and Li Wenhui
just want an apology.

708
00:38:04,599 --> 00:38:05,360
Is that too much?

709
00:38:06,079 --> 00:38:07,519
Just because you're from the city,

710
00:38:07,519 --> 00:38:08,679
you twist right and wrong around.

711
00:38:08,880 --> 00:38:10,239
We just want an apology.

712
00:38:10,960 --> 00:38:13,599
Say sorry! Apologize!

713
00:38:13,599 --> 00:38:14,119
Shut up.

714
00:38:14,119 --> 00:38:15,280
Say sorry to us.

715
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:16,280
Shut up.

716
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:17,119
Shut your mouths.

717
00:38:17,320 --> 00:38:20,480
Apologize now! Say sorry!

718
00:38:20,519 --> 00:38:21,599
Shut your mouths.

719
00:38:21,639 --> 00:38:23,039
Say sorry! Apologize!

720
00:38:23,039 --> 00:38:23,840
Shut up.

721
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:27,000
Apologize! Say sorry!

722
00:38:27,039 --> 00:38:27,800
Shut up.

723
00:38:27,880 --> 00:38:29,599
Say sorry! Apologize!

724
00:38:29,599 --> 00:38:30,159
Come with me.

725
00:38:30,239 --> 00:38:35,039
Apologize! Say sorry!

726
00:38:59,599 --> 00:39:00,480
What happened to Qing Ye?

727
00:39:00,679 --> 00:39:01,119
Xing Wu.
Where are you going?

728
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:25,159
That's too much.

729
00:39:25,760 --> 00:39:27,320
Too much?

730
00:39:27,480 --> 00:39:28,320
The teacher is here.

731
00:39:28,320 --> 00:39:29,920
Who bullies people like that?

732
00:39:30,239 --> 00:39:31,519
Bullying people?

733
00:39:38,239 --> 00:39:38,920
What are you doing?

734
00:39:42,840 --> 00:39:43,440
It's the cafeteria.
It's for eating.

735
00:39:45,840 --> 00:39:47,119
Let me remind you.

736
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:49,840
Each of you

737
00:39:49,840 --> 00:39:50,440
only gets

738
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:51,880
one shot at high school.

739
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:55,000
Don't do something

740
00:39:55,000 --> 00:39:56,320
you'll still regret

741
00:39:57,039 --> 00:39:58,000
years after graduation.

742
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:39,679
I'll pack it for you.

743
00:41:27,320 --> 00:41:27,840
Hungry?

744
00:41:29,320 --> 00:41:29,880
Try it.

745
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:31,480
What is this?

746
00:41:32,119 --> 00:41:33,440
Seaweed jelly.

747
00:41:33,960 --> 00:41:34,840
A local specialty.

748
00:41:37,400 --> 00:41:37,960
Go on. Eat.
It's not poisoned.

749
00:41:49,480 --> 00:41:50,159
It's salty.

750
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:52,400
Good, right?

751
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:00,480
Weren't you going with Shu Han

752
00:42:00,480 --> 00:42:01,480
to meet Mr. Ye?

753
00:42:02,199 --> 00:42:03,000
Why are you here?

754
00:42:04,320 --> 00:42:05,079
What a coincidence.

755
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:06,639
Just passing by.

756
00:42:14,119 --> 00:42:16,079
Wu, emergency.

757
00:42:16,280 --> 00:42:17,199
Qing Ye's in trouble.

758
00:42:17,400 --> 00:42:18,039
Qing Ye,
You stained

759
00:42:19,039 --> 00:42:19,880
Li Wenhui's clothes.
I have to go.

760
00:42:21,039 --> 00:42:21,760
Something urgent.

761
00:42:23,000 --> 00:42:24,239
What about Mr. Ye?

762
00:42:24,320 --> 00:42:25,039
You know this chance
is rare.

763
00:42:26,079 --> 00:42:27,239
Please apologize to him for me.

764
00:42:27,400 --> 00:42:28,400
I'll make it up next time.

765
00:42:28,599 --> 00:42:29,159
Xing Wu.

766
00:42:32,719 --> 00:42:33,719
I thought

767
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:36,880
once I got to Zhazhating,

768
00:42:37,840 --> 00:42:39,480
everything would be over.

769
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:42,119
I could start over.

770
00:42:48,159 --> 00:42:49,159
This is a small place.

771
00:42:50,199 --> 00:42:51,239
The tiniest thing

772
00:42:51,599 --> 00:42:53,239
spreads through town fast.

773
00:42:53,840 --> 00:42:55,320
People don't have much to do.

774
00:42:55,960 --> 00:42:56,960
They love watching drama.

775
00:42:57,679 --> 00:42:58,360
They hear a story,

776
00:42:58,599 --> 00:42:59,840
spice it up,

777
00:43:00,039 --> 00:43:01,039
make things up,

778
00:43:01,039 --> 00:43:02,280
then pass lies off as truth.

779
00:43:03,039 --> 00:43:04,599
The stranger, the better.

780
00:43:05,039 --> 00:43:05,639
Exactly.

781
00:43:06,440 --> 00:43:07,679
They don't care about the truth.

782
00:43:08,679 --> 00:43:09,639
But they forget fast.

783
00:43:10,039 --> 00:43:11,599
A few days later, new gossip comes,

784
00:43:11,880 --> 00:43:13,679
and the old story is gone.

785
00:43:15,079 --> 00:43:15,920
Don't take it to heart.

786
00:43:17,039 --> 00:43:18,079
People who spread rumors forget.

787
00:43:18,599 --> 00:43:19,960
But the people they hurt?

788
00:43:20,920 --> 00:43:22,159
What about their pain?

789
00:43:30,079 --> 00:43:30,880
What are you doing?

790
00:43:31,920 --> 00:43:32,599
Close your eyes.

791
00:43:33,239 --> 00:43:33,960
Close your eyes.

792
00:43:43,679 --> 00:43:44,440
Take a deep breath.

